  <description type="morphology">Leaf blades 5–18 × 1–5+ cm. Ray laminae 6–15 mm. Disc corollas 3.5–6 mm. Cypselae 3–5 mm. 2n = ca. 40, ca. 50–54, 50–58, 56, ca. 56, 57, and 60.</description>
